      "15": "kai exeklinan ekei kai eishlqosan eis ton oikon tou paidariou tou leuitou eis ton oikon mica kai hspasanto auton",
      "16": "kai oi exakosioi andres periezwsmenoi skeuh polemika esthlwmenoi para thn quran tou pulwnos oi ek twn uiwn dan",
      "17": "kai anebhsan oi pente andres oi poreuomenoi kataskeyasqai thn ghn epelqontes ekei elabon to glupton kai to efoud kai to qerafin kai to cwneuton kai o iereus esthlwmenos para th qura tou pulwnos kai oi exakosioi andres oi periezwsmenoi skeuh polemika",
