      "19": "kai eipan pros auton kwfeuson epiqes thn ceira sou epi to stoma sou kai elqe meq hmwn kai esh hmin eis patera kai eis ierea mh beltion einai se ierea oikou andros enos h ginesqai se ierea fulhs kai suggeneias en israhl",
